---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Student Life | Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad"
	description="Discover student life at Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College — sports, cultural programs, clubs, competitions, educational tours, and leadership opportunities."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	 <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Student Life</span></div>
      <h1>Student Life</h1>
      <p>School is more than textbooks. Here's how our students play, perform, compete, and grow beyond the classroom.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517486808906-6ca8b3f04846?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Students participating in a school sports competition" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Play, Compete, Grow</span>
        <h2>Sports Activities</h2>
        <p class="lede">Physical education is a core part of the school day. Students take part in athletics, cricket, football, kabaddi, badminton, and yoga, with structured house-level and inter-school competitions each year.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Daily physical education periods for all classes</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Annual sports meet with district-level participation</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Four school houses competing across the academic year</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container split reverse-mobile">
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541339907198-e08756dedf3f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Students performing at the school annual day function" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">A Campus That Celebrates</span>
        <h2>Annual Functions &amp; Cultural Programs</h2>
        <p class="lede">Our Annual Day, Independence Day, Republic Day, and Saraswati Puja celebrations bring the entire school community together through music, dance, drama, and student-led performances.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Annual Day showcase featuring every class</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Inter-house cultural competitions throughout the year</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Festival celebrations rooted in Indian tradition and values</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Find Your Passion</span>
        <h2>Student Clubs</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 2v6.34a2 2 0 0 1-.24.96L3.6 18.4A2 2 0 0 0 5.36 21.5h13.28a2 2 0 0 0 1.76-3.1l-5.16-9.1a2 2 0 0 1-.24-.96V2"/><path d="M6.5 2h11"/><path d="M6.5 12.5h11"/></svg></div><h4>Science Club</h4><p>Experiments, projects, and exhibition preparation.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="13.5" cy="6.5" r=".5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="10.5" r=".5"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="7.5" r=".5"/><circle cx="6.5" cy="12.5" r=".5"/><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0 0 20 2 2 0 0 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0-4h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2c0-5.5-4.5-10-10-10Z"/></svg></div><h4>Art &amp; Craft Club</h4><p>Painting, sketching, and creative expression.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg></div><h4>Music &amp; Dance Club</h4><p>Classical and contemporary performance training.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></div><h4>Literary &amp; Debate Club</h4><p>Elocution, debate, and creative writing practice.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Beyond the Campus</span>
        <h2>Competitions &amp; Educational Tours</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/><path d="M7 4h10v5a5 5 0 0 1-10 0Z"/><path d="M17 5.5h2.5a2 2 0 0 1 0 4H17"/><path d="M7 5.5H4.5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4H7"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Competitions</h3>
          <p>Students regularly participate in inter-school science olympiads, sports tournaments, elocution contests, and district-level cultural competitions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Educational Tours</h3>
          <p>Age-appropriate excursions — from local nature walks for primary students to educational trips to museums, science centres, and historical sites for seniors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Leading From the Front</span>
        <h2>Leadership &amp; Co-Curricular Programs</h2>
        <p class="lede">We give students real responsibility. Our Student Council, House Captains, and NCC unit build leadership, teamwork, and civic responsibility from an early age.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Elected Student Council with real decision-making input</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> NCC unit for Class 9 and above</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> House Captain and Prefect system across all wings</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Community service and social awareness drives</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547153760-18fc86324498?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Students rehearsing a dance performance" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Recognising Our Students</span>
        <h2>Student Achievements</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card card-ribbon reveal" data-ribbon="Gold"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.5 13.5 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.5-8.5"/></svg></div><h3>State Science Olympiad</h3><p>Three students represented Uttar Pradesh at the national qualifier round in 2025.</p></div>
        <div class="card card-ribbon reveal" data-ribbon="Champion"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/><path d="M7 4h10v5a5 5 0 0 1-10 0Z"/><path d="M17 5.5h2.5a2 2 0 0 1 0 4H17"/><path d="M7 5.5H4.5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4H7"/></svg></div><h3>District Kabaddi Championship</h3><p>Under-17 boys' team won the district title for the second consecutive year.</p></div>
        <div class="card card-ribbon reveal" data-ribbon="1st Place"><div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.5 13.5 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.5-8.5"/></svg></div><h3>Inter-School Debate Competition</h3><p>Senior team secured first place at the Ghaziabad zonal-level debate meet.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
